title: Trump Goes on Vacation While His Team Debuts So-Called "Real News" | Billy Eichner
description:
Seth takes a closer look at the Trump team's effort to ramp up attacks on the Russia probe and news media despite the President being on vacation. (0:20)
Then, Billy Eichner explains how he used Trump to campaign for Billy on the Street's first Emmy nomination and lays out strong arguments for why he deserves to win his category over Saturday Night Live. (12:18)
